  <summary date="2018-09-27T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Senior Scams Prevention Act

This bill establishes a Senior Scams Prevention Advisory Council, which shall create&#160;model educational materials to&#160;educate&#160;employees of&#160;retailers, financial-services companies,&#160;and wire-transfer companies on how to identify and prevent scams that affect seniors.</summary>
